aVWe also tried to take a more directly intellectual approach
p193
aVwith the genomes of 13 related organisms,
p194
aVand we tried to compare all of those, to see what they had in common.
p195
aVAnd we got these overlapping circles. And we found only 173 genes
p196
aVcommon to all 13 organisms.
